{"article_id":"361u1FiY7suNLsrb","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Get all the latest news on coronavirus and more delivered daily to your inbox .","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"Sign up here .","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"The United States has reached a grim milestone in the fight against coronavirus ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"passing Italy","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"to become the country with the most deaths in the world .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"A tally by Johns Hopkins University showed Saturday","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"that 18,860 people have now died in the U.S. since the start of the outbreak .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"On Saturday , 2,108 people died in the U.S. in the past 24 hours","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"- the first country in the world","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"to record more than 2,000 deaths in a single day .","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"As a result , the U.S. has now overtaken Italy 's total of 18,849 .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"It has recorded more than 503,000 cases .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"The pandemic ' s epicenter has long shifted to Europe and the U.S. ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"which also now has by far the largest number of confirmed cases , with more than half a million .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"It saw more than 35,000 new positive infections in the last 24 hours ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"according to Johns Hopkins University .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"However , experts on the White House ' s coronavirus task force suggested","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"the outbreak within America ' s borders is starting to level off slowly .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"\" As encouraging as they are ,","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"we have not reached the peak , \"","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Dr. Deborah Birx said Friday .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Meanwhile , President Donald Trump insisted","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"he would not reopen the country","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"until it is safe .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"\" I want to get it open as soon as possible , \"","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"he said at a Good Friday briefing","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"while adding :","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"\" The facts are going to determine what I do . \"","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"AMERICA","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"RELEARNING THE LESSONS OF THE 1918 SPANISH FLU PANDEMIC","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"More than 40 percent of the deaths in the U.S. have happened in New York state ,","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"which is considered the epicenter of the virus in the country .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"On Saturday , New York City Mayor Bill de Blasio announced","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"that the city ' s public schools will be shuttered for the rest of the academic year .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"online education will continue for the 1.1 million-student district .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"School buildings in New York City have been closed since March 16 .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"The state has been the worst hit in the country , with 8,627 deaths as of Saturday .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"De Blasio praised teachers for what he said","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"was a heroic effort","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"to teach their students online , a practice","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"that has been met with mixed success","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"as many of the city ' s low-income students lack Wi-Fi and devices","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"for connecting to their virtual classrooms .","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"\" Our educators were asked to learn an entirely different way of teaching , \"","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"\" And they weren ' t given a year","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"to get ready .","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"They weren ' t given a month","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"to get ready .","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"They had a week","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"to quickly retool","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"and turn to distance learning , online learning","depth":13},{"id":53,"text":"and make it work . \"","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"Hours later , however , Gov . Andrew Cuomo said","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"there had been no decision made","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"on closing the schools yet .","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"\" There ' s been no decision on schools , \"","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"Cuomo said in Albany at his daily coronavirus briefing .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"Cuomo said of de Blasio ,","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"\" He didn ' t close them","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"and he can ' t open them . \"","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"Other states","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"including Virginia , Pennsylvania , and Vermont","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"have previously announced","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"that schools will be shuttered for the rest of the year .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"Health experts have warned","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"if the country rolls back restrictions too quickly ,","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"case levels could once again begin to soar ,","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"especially without widespread testing","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"to determine who might be a carrier of the virus .","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"Dr. Anthony Fauci , the nation ' s top infectious-diseases expert , said this week","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"that a timeline","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"for reopening the country","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"would entail reviewing the data day-by-day .","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"\" The virus kind of decides whether or not it ' s appropriate to open it , \"","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"he told CNN .","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"\" The one thing","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"you don ' t want to do","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"is you don ' t want to get out there prematurely","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"and then wind up backtracking . \"","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"More than 1.7 million people have been infected with coronavirus worldwide .","depth":3},{"id":83,"text":"More than 100,000 have died ,","depth":4},{"id":84,"text":"while more than 388,000 have recovered from the illness .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":169,"left":86,"right":168,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":86,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":168,"left":165,"right":167,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":165,"left":111,"right":164,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":111,"left":95,"right":110,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":88,"right":94,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":88,"left":2,"right":87,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":87,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":92,"right":93,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":92,"left":89,"right":91,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":89,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":91,"left":7,"right":90,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":98,"right":109,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":98,"left":96,"right":97,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":102,"right":108,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":102,"left":99,"right":101,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":101,"left":100,"right":20,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent